verses.text:
For there is no <i>[f]</i>faithfulness in their mouth;
Their inward part is <i>[g]</i>very wickedness;
 Their throat is an open sepulchre;
 They <i>[h]</i>flatter with their tongue.

Hold them guilty, O God;
Let them fall <i>[i]</i>by their own counsels;
  Thrust them out in the multitude of their transgressions;
  For they have rebelled against thee.
